org.jarreader.visitor.impl

Class DisassembleVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.bcel.classfile.EmptyVisitor
      • org.jarreader.visitor.JarVisitor
        • org.jarreader.visitor.impl.DisassembleVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.bcel.classfile.Visitor

    public class DisassembleVisitor
extends JarVisitor
    Visitor for disassembling classes in JAR. Class is represented as compilable Java source code, but instructions are shown as commented out JVM Assembly code, recreating the functionality of javap utility.
